@* Page to add a new vendor by filling out a form. Once complete will route back to homepage *@
@* Routed from /vendors back, this is vendors/new and will have two buttons. One to SUBMIT a new vendor and one to CANCEL. Both will route back to homepage *@

<h1>Add a Vendor</h1>
<h4>Vendor Information:</h4>

<form action="/vendors" method="POST">
  <label for="vendorName">Vendor Name</label>
  <input id="vendorName" name="vendorName" type="text">
  <button type="submit">Add</button>
</form>

<p><a href="/vendors">Cancel</a> and return to Vendor list.</p>
<p><a href="/">Home.</a></p>